{"tid":1753744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（區選之後）預測建制派覆桌運作模式","createTime":"2019-11-25T04:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T04:56:37.000Z","uid":54442,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"657a0d594b5c450e6e4f7fcd6677a3c749002efc","tid":1753744,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:21:10.000Z","msg":"百足之蟲 死而不僵<br />\n建制派點都會無孔不入地加強攻勢<br />\n<br />\n1. 例如運用現有立法會議員辦事處，將落選議員搖身一變做議員助理，繼續做事。<br />\n2. 政府總部有很多諮詢委員會，全部政府委任，將成為各未來出選人士的踏板<br />\n3. 錢，阿爺大把錢，極平價本地一日團向婆仔招徠<br />\n4. 更強大的地區支持者資料庫，以便配票<br />\n5. 具爭議政府政策或會繞過區議會，直上立法會<br />\n6. 控制傳媒，向大眾渲染政府想發出的訊息<br />\n7. 舊議員辦事處會繼續續租予建制衛星團體<br />\n<br />\n方法真係仲有好多，各位和理非往後不能鬆懈，唔好一味靠議員，睇實自己住的選區！"},{"pid":"f04ccf5b628b7acde9008185c75ab721805e15e6","tid":1753744,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:22:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"871135e5b487183d80e76bce20ccceb5d605af05","tid":1753744,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfd63784d528845c63ef16166186e4af6b5cf73","tid":1753744,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:24:00.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"273a396d91b457113b53975e7e29e47867efd0ce","tid":1753744,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:25:27.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"21358c7d45806082251e8d35d08652fe904c4332","tid":1753744,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:27:45.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"18c0b3255205cc6333c97c13c12bbd85abc9b581","tid":1753744,"uid":273409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:28:15.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40341bae0a8b2ea0577fe378a1f39ef3833f3a9","tid":1753744,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:30:1